      "content": "i really dont want to go to the er if i can help it, its so expensive and the wait is always hours. i have some heavy duty migraine meds from my doctor though. if i just take a double dose of those and lay in a dark room, do you think that would fix the face thing too? maybe it's just a weird muscle spasm from the pain?",
